&lt;p id="8gAPVM"&gt;Applications will be open from Thursday, October 10th, at 11AM ET to Tuesday, October 15th, at 10:59AM ET. You can apply by clicking the “To Application Page” link &lt;a href="https://playtest-p.nintendo.com/en-us"&gt;on this page&lt;/a&gt;....&lt;/p&gt;
